question: Where can I find restaurant on the route to Hidden Lake Metropark, Leroy Township, OH within 190 kilometers from Graffiti Wall, Erie, PA?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-80.081842 42.120204)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-81.131586 41.682725)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-80.081842 42.120204)',4326)::geography, 190000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-80.081842 42.120204)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
